'''''Akka''''' is a [[1976 in film|1976]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]], [[Film director|directed]] by Madurai Thirumaran and produced by Mathura Films. It stars [[K. R. Vijaya]], [[Vijayakumar (actor)|Vijayakumar]], Vijayabala and [[Jai Ganesh]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Akka Vinyl LP Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/33/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424010741/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F33%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=24 April 2014|dead-url=yes|df=dmy-all}}</ref>

